##### FOLDER ARCHITECURE #####


(public): [ALL PAGES]
  [PAGE]: has view and bloc folder

  auth: [before login pages]:
    - signup
    - signin
    ...

  dashboard: [after login pages]
    - home
    - user
    ...

_____________________________________________


blocs: [GLOBAL MANAGEMENT STATE]
  blocs per data:
    - user
    - categories
    ...

_____________________________________________


core: [CORE]
  - utils
  - constants
  ...

_____________________________________________


data: [API integration and data management]
  - adapter
  - models
  - repositories
  - services

_____________________________________________


presentation: [Visual and presentation components of the application.]
  - components
  - layouts
  - screens
  - theme
